Deus Ex GO Version 2.0
PUZZLE MAKER UPDATE

-Puzzle Maker feature: create and share your very own puzzles
-Highly requested Undo feature: use it to go back step by step in any puzzle
-Profile page: earn XP, level up and earn rewards
-New Daily Challenge to test your skills
-Improved shopping experience
-Various improvements and fixes

Thanks for playing Deus Ex GO, we are excited to be able to put our tools in your hands, and we’re eager to play your puzzles!

Tons of great puzzles are created every day by the community. Thank you for your continued support! 

- Puzzle creator's name is now displayed properly
- Walker AI now behaves as expected when blocked on both sides
- Various bug fixes and improvements
